03/05/76 add_line_numbers, aln

Function: adds a new set of line numbers to the specified segment.


Syntax:  aln {path} {new_number increment}


Arguments:
path   pathname of segment; if omitted, temporary text is used.

new_number   first line to be added (default is 100).

increment   increment used to derive subsequent line numbers; can
only be used with new_number  (default is 10).


